Package: tessera
Title: Genomic-Driven Biomarker Identification for Colorectal Cancer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Principal", "Statistician", , "stats@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A statistics-focused R package supporting the in-silico validation
    of a colorectal-cancer polygenic risk score (CRC-PRS) as a genetically
    anchored stratification signal for circulating CEA, using a simulated
    UK-Biobank-like clinical cohort. Provides utilities to simulate the
    cohort, fit linear and logistic regression models, run interaction
    tests, and produce publication-ready plots for Quarto reporting.
